    {
      "text": "The sequel to Spectral Force is set in a fantasy world called Neverland. The ruler of Demon Kingdom was defeated by the hero Chiffon, leaving behind a son and a daughter, the children of his human wife.\n\nThe two half-demons strive to regain the lost power. The sister Hiro re-builds the Demon Kingdom, while the brother Jadou finds a way to communicate with our world, and summons a Japanese schoolgirl who soon becomes a mighty warrior under his guidance.",
